---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout>
  <main class="min-h-dvh p-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto flex flex-col justify-center">
    <section
      class="prose prose-lg prose-neutral dark:prose-invert prose-a:font-medium">
      <div class="flex justify-between gap-2 flex-wrap">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-display dark:text-neutral-200">
          Andrew Monty
        </h1>
        <div class="flex gap-3 flex-wrap">
          <a href="/resume">Resum√©</a>
          <a href="/work">Work</a>
          <a href="/gear">Gear</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
        <span class="flex text-sm rounded-full border border-zinc-600">
          <span class="px-2 py-0.5">designer</span>
          <div class="w-px bg-zinc-600 inset-y-0 transform -skew-12"></div>
          <span class="px-2 py-0.5">developer</span>
          <div class="w-px bg-zinc-600 inset-y-0 transform -skew-12"></div>
          <span class="px-2 py-0.5">devops</span>
          <div class="w-px bg-zinc-600 inset-y-0 transform -skew-12"></div>
          <a href="https://amplinks.app" class="px-2 py-0.5">@ Amplinks</a>
        </span>
      </div>
      <p>
        Started tinkering with the web by customizing my myspace page, and
        somehow made a career of it! I love how open and approachable the web
        is, it's so easy to get some pixels on a screen, but also incredibly
        powerful!
      </p>

      <p>
        In my free time I enjoy a good beer on a patio, getting lost in an
        immersive rpg, and dogs! Gilly volunteers at the library and
        <a
          href="https://public.tableau.com/shared/XXKKT25DK?:display_count=y&:origin=viz_share_link&:embed=y">
          competes in toss & fetch
        </a>
        .
      </p>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
